Seasoned Marksman;;1;For every 6 enemy Minion or Mercenary kills near your Hero, gain 1 Basic Attack damage. Hero Takedowns count as 2 Minion kills.
Demolitionist;;1;Basic Attacks against Structures destroy 1 ammo and deal an additional 10% damage.
Bribe;;1;Kill enemy Minions to gain stacks of Bribe. Use 20 stacks to bribe target Mercenary, instantly defeating them. Does not work on Golems.
Scouting Drone;;1;Places a Scouting Drone at target location, revealing a large area around it for 60 seconds. This drone can be seen and killed by enemies. 60s cooldown.
Advanced Optics;;4;Increases your Basic Attack range by 20%.
Focused Attack;;4;Every 10 seconds, your next Basic Attack deals 50% additional damage. Basic Attacks reduce this cooldown by 1 second.
Vampiric Assault;;4;Basic Attacks heal for 15% of the damage dealt.
Quick Fingers (Trait);;4;Doubles the cooldown reduction of Lead From the Front.
Heavy Ammo;;7;Penetrating Round has increased knock back distance, and deals 100% extra damage to structures.
Revolution Overdrive;;7;Gain 10% Movement Speed when using Inspire, plus 5% additional Movement Speed for each ally Hero Inspired.
Fight or Flight;;7;Adrenaline Rush cleanses all movement impairing effects, and makes you Unstoppable for 2 seconds.
Searing Attacks;;7;Activate to increase Basic Attack damage by 50% for 5 seconds. Each attack costs 15 Mana. 25s cooldown.
Hyperion;;10;Call down the Hyperion which slowly travels across the battleground dealing 25 damage to up to 4 random enemy targets in its path. Lasts for 12 seconds. 100s cooldown.
Raynor's Raiders;;10;Summons two cloaked Banshees that follow you for a short time and attack what you attack. Each Banshee attacks for 2 volleys of 10 damage each.
Giant Killer;;10;Basic Attacks against enemy Heroes deal bonus damage equal to 1.5% of the Hero's max Health.
The Art of War;;10;On using Inspire, nearby enemies have their Attack Speed and Movement Speed lowered by 10%.
Activated Rush;;10;Adrenaline Rush can be used on command. Doing so reduces the cooldown by 15 seconds.
Spell Shield;;10;Upon taking Ability Damage, reduce all Ability Damage taken by 50% for 2 seconds. Can only trigger once every 30 seconds.
